# Real (non-example) configs — must stay local. .env-style: copy *.example.* to non-example, edit.
**/config/mcp-config.json
**/config/planning-preferences.md
**/config/settings.conf
**/memory/memory.md
**/logs/
**/.last-run/
**/.tmp/

# Local (personalized) prompt body — see prompts/cron-prompt.example.md for the template
prompts/cron-prompt.md

# launchd plists (user-specific paths)
**/launchd/com.*.plist
!**/launchd/*.plist.example

# Codex-side artifacts that leak local paths
**/automation.toml
!**/automation.example.toml
**/agents/*.yaml
!**/agents/*.example.yaml

# OAuth and credential files (should NEVER be in repo regardless)
**/credentials.json
**/token.json
*.pem
*.key

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*~

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
venv/
